data.description: Great all brick 3 bed 2 bath home convenient to all 3 universities and the capitol. This light & bright home features hardwood floors (carpet free), multiple living spaces, formal dining and an open eat-in kitchen An abundance of windows allow for highly desired natural light throughout the home and lead out to the sunroom/office overlooking the private fenced in backyard (Perfect for entertaining!) Other features include a 2-car carport along with ample driveway parking, 2 storage sheds, updated Stainless steel appliances, and a wood burning fireplace.  Roof 2016 & Hot Water Heater 2019. Great for owner occupants and investors, this one won't last long!
